28:02.060 --> 28:10.160
to society who wants change. The ideas that Highland put across with free love and sex and the

28:10.160 --> 28:16.280
novel also had a great deal to do with some of the changing mores in the 60s. Some people have seen a

28:17.240 --> 28:25.700
heavily symbolic value to Smith. He is killed by earth people who are afraid of his movement

28:26.300 --> 28:31.320
but he has the ability as taught to him by the old ones on Mars to overcome death,

28:32.320 --> 28:37.060
sort of a resurrection, not his physical body as such but a new state of being.

28:37.500 --> 28:42.300
And I think that some people see that as almost a Christ symbol. You have a leader with special powers,

28:43.120 --> 28:50.140
